for (i in 1:15){

N <- rpois(1,1000)
Ax <- c()
Ay <- c()

while (length(Ax)<N){
  u <- runif(2,min=-2*pi,max=2*pi)
  if(rbinom(1,1,sin(sqrt(u[1]^2+u[2]^2)-3.14*i/15)^4)){
    Ax <- c(Ax,u[1])
    Ay <- c(Ay,u[2])
  }
}

plot(Ax,Ay,
     asp=1,
     xlab="x",
     ylab="y",
     pch=20
     )
  
}

for(i in 1:15){
  #find number of points
  n <- rpois(1,10)
  
  #place the points
  x <- rep(-1,n) 
  for(j in 1:n){
    while(x[j]==-1){
      point <- c(runif(1,0,1),runif(1,0,20))
      if(point[2]<(10*(1-cos(4*pi*point[1])))){
        x[j] <- point[1]
      }
    }
  }
  
  #plot the set of points
  t<-seq(0,1,length.out=300)
  plot(x,rep(0,n),
       pch=16,
       xlim=c(0,1),
       ylim=c(-0.5,2),
       xlab="", 
       ylab="")+
    lines(t,(1-cos(4*pi*t)))
    
}
